resource.description: The idea behind Kundera is to make working with NoSQL Databases drop-dead simple and fun. Kundera is being developed with following objectives: * To make working with NoSQL as simple as working with SQL * To serve as JPA Compliant mapping solution for NoSQL Datastores. * To help developers, forget the complexity of NoSQL stores and focus on Domain Model. * To make switching across data-stores as easy as changing a configuration.
